		FlowHat Blog may include outbound links to marketplaces, software vendors, or service providers.
	</p>
	<ul>
		<li>Some links may later become affiliate links.</li>
		<li>If that happens, the site may earn a commission from qualifying purchases.</li>
		<li>Editorial decisions are intended to remain independent of affiliate relationships.</li>
	</ul>
	<p>
		At the moment, marketplace links on the site may still be plain outbound links while monetization
		setup is being prepared.
	</p>
	<p>
		If display advertising such as Google AdSense is enabled later, this page will be updated to
		reflect that clearly.
	</p>
</PageLayout>
